I"í<p>Later today, the Office of Li Zhaozhi will release General Principles that will guide professional and personal development from 2021 to 2023. These principles will be generally applicable to all aspects of life, from work to home.</p>

<p>In addition to guiding principles, the document will also provide tools for putting the principles into action. After the release of the General Principles, the Office will also release its first three-year Career Plan and learning plan covering 2021 to 2023. Companion with the Career Plan will be a Learning Plan listing knowledge and skills required for career advancement and steps to obtain these resources.</p>

<p>These documents are critical in the sense that they will induce meaningful changes and align behaviour closer to objectives and goals in professional and personal lives. These documents will contain important information and be featured on the website during their effective period.</p>

